Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:48.50,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:57.30,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.68,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.82,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
Comment: 0,0:24:29.25,0:24:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{ed end}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After dueling, Benio used her tomboyish two-handed fencing and beat the boastful Count with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,These two began to celebrate,\Nconcluding that it'd spell Benio's imminent return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold your horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For the Count saw his long-gone son's\Nlook in Benio's eyes, and was charmed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, Benio's special herbal medicine\Nhelped the Count open his heart up to the Countess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, the flame of the\Nelderly couple's love is rekindled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversely, Benio's own betrothed doesn't seem\Nto mind the arranged marriage forced upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a man after that? Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for today's training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome. Make sure they perfect\Nthat technique for next month's rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Fujieda Ranmaru,\Nthe young kabuki dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! He's fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,,And a young teacher, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.56,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even leave after class in peace anymore.{うっかりお稽古にも出られやしないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do all girls have to be like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what they do,\NI would never love a girl other than Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want them. No sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A delicious man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, you're a sight for sore eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.82,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ranmaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Get a grip, dammit! You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, how did you\Nmiss me if we meet everyday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I still missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it to yourself. \NI'm not into that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What does that mean, Ushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, nothin' special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushi, how's Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, our manly Boss \Nhas become unrecognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks completely emaciated and broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio... Moving to an unfamiliar mansion\Nbelonging to nobility was too much for you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to do something about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, please go see her at the mansion for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.{僕なんだか胸騒ぎがするの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd gladly go there, but I don't have\Nto bring her to school since it's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're refusing me this little favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. It's not the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my methods, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What methods?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Molester here! A molester!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being molested!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's molesting me—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it! \NI'll go, now calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is why you're the best!{だからうしさんって大好き}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they getting ready for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,An open-air party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? An open-air party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a closed door party.\NOnly my close friends are invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all awfully\Nexcited to meet my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... H-Hey, I object!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm your fiancée, um...{婚約者と言っても、あの。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still not agreed to this marriage.{あの、アタシはまだ結婚を承知したわけでは。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be so stiff about it, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't you just laugh my opinion off like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he always so self-centered?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears the Boss is heated today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru's feminine intuition was right.{蘭丸の女性的な感は大したもん}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a guy, but whatever. I need to inform him.{あいつは男だったがともかく知らせてこなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ushigorou, right?{もしうしごろさんでしたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a rush, so I'll see ya later.{なんか呼んだら後にしてくんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't tolerate it any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you being too rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, because you're\Nencroaching on my profession!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha sayin'?! Whaddya mean by that?{なんだと何を言いちゃも----}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, please stop carrying\NLady Benio to school on your rickshaw!{うしごろうさん、べにおさまを人力者で学校へ送り迎えするのは\やめてください}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Are you out of your tiny mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a very important lady for this family.{あの方はご当家にとって大切なお人です}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's plainly obvious\Nthat {\i1}I{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}escort her with the Ijuuins' car!{さすれば私が伊集院家のこの車で送り迎えさせていただく のが理の当然}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!\NThink you can boss me around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't agree soon, I'll have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between\Nagreeing quickly and slowly, you idiot?!{早く申し立て遅く申し立て同じだよこの馬鹿野郎}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've agreed!{ではご了承願いましたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're just trying to sow discord\Nbetween me and the Boss, but I ain't falling for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a rush now, but I'll be sure to\Ncome set things straight with you later! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whassup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ijuuin, where's your fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio's her name, right? C'mon, introduce us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your beautiful Mädchen? {どこだその麗しのメッチェン - I wanted to keep the German reference}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beautiful?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were into these things.{お前この趣味だったのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lolita complex, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Lolita complex it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Lolita complex,\Nand borderline boys' love on top of it.{すなわち少年愛に通じる}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For boys! For boys! {no idea but better than leaving it out completely}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies! I only meant to praise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, this is Takayashiki, a buddy of mine.{べにおさんこちら僕の親友で高屋敷です}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sharp-tongued, but he's really a nice guy.{口は悪いがいいやつですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was sharp, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, it's the same Boozy Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,An outdoor party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, lots of people are there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably. I hope the Boss\Nwon't feel too awkward there.{多分な親分がうまく立ち回ってくるといいんだけどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not so good with social skills.{あんまり社交は上手な方じゃねえからなうちの親分は}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a party, there'll also be alcohol, right?{それと園遊会といえばお酒も出るんでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boss has a really bad\Ninclination for drunken violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad! We gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, can you think of something?
Comment: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me. I have a wonderful idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll work out for sure!{こうしちゃ入れられないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, \Nbut I just can't stop worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Takayashiki Kaname—he wants to be a poet.{この高屋敷要は文士くずれでね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,His pen name is Lionmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I feel like no further explanation is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting me, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the beautiful Tamaki!{いやいや、麗しの環殿}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our angel!{我らの天使}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddess!{女神ちゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, come with me for a second.{べにおさんもその後いかがお少し}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that request?{何をその気取った挨拶}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, what happened\Nto your breaking mission? {べにお、どうしたのよ例の作戦}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight is on and\Nthe enemy won't yield an inch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tough one.{我苦戦なり}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still trying my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ho... this conversation between classmates sure is getting lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Benio was telling me about all\Nthe gossips permeating the Count's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you two.{さあさあお二人さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls shouldn't abandon the party like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we play a game?{ゲームでもしませんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tamaki, I wrote a poem for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to let me read it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidelined twice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unrequited love is the truest one. \NI'll write an even better poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming today.{今日はよくいらっしゃいました}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy your time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So... there's something I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer\Nwill you keep detaining Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything.{私知ってますのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Benio's betrothed simply because your grandmother said so, not because you love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But Benio's not the right person for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu... There must be someone who's better\Nsuited for you, both in their mind and descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't you feel bad for Benio going through all\Nthe difficulties of learning to live in a noble house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's gossiping about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A noble house, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You descend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,from a noble family, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki, you need to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that we were born into noble families...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The privilege of high descent—\Nwe owe it all to chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have to live our lives brandishing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ever wanted was to escape this bizarre world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But... ever since I met Benio,{でも紅緒さんに会ってから}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that this boundary \Ncould be crossed, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what I intend to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a girl who, having seen a dream once, \Ncan easily make that dream a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In that sense, I just keep seeing dreams, \Nbut do nothing about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, at first, I only wanted\Nto do it for my grandmother.{確かに僕も最初はおばあ様のためにと考えていた}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But things have changed.{でも今は違う}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio has this mysterious charm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've never felt in any other girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu—deep down, you've\Nalways wanted someone like Benio.{忍さん、心のどこかでいつもべにおを望んでいたのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place for me in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you now.{わかったわしのぶさんの気持ち}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fantastic girl too, \Nso you'll definitely find a fantastic partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have given up.{私諦めた}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is my best friend.{べにおは私の親友ですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever make her sad, I...{あの人を不幸せにしたら私が承知。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!{承知しませんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:15:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bother. Where did those two go?{しょうがないな2人ともどこ行っちゃったのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shinobu! \NHe's never done anything like that to me!{少尉ったらあんなこと私には一度だってしてくれたことないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she better than me?{差がついてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What could those two be talking about?{あの2人何話してるんだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki is so beautiful...{綺麗だなたまき}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's better suited for Shinobu than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see, Tamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hey... Whaddya want? \NWhat did I do?{なんだって言うんだ俺が何をしたってんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. What's wrong with you two? Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, cut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea. By now, these dogs\Nshould know Takayashiki rather well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ijuuin, do something!{おい伊集院なんとかしろよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to this house countless times,{僕はこの家へなんでも来てるし}\Nbut I don't remember ever being barked at!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you don't believe my best friend's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the unadulterated\Ninstinct of these two better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be sensing something\Nabnormal about Takayashiki today.{今日に限って\N高屋敷さんに吠えるのは何か異常を感じているからです}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I still believe these dogs. \NTenmaru, Chimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush! Hush! I'm telling you to hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!\NBenio, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? \NThey'd rather listen to Benio than to me...{なんということだ僕よりも紅緒さんの言うことを聞くなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takayashiki, \Nthere's something on your back.{おい高屋敷お前の背中に何かいるぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A wasp!{クマンバチだ - technically a carpenter bee}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't taken a bath in ten days,\N{俺は十日も風呂に入ってないんだよ }I'll be doomed if I get stung!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! It left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Their stings would hurt like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such good dogs! So you weren't\Nbarking at Takayashiki, but at the wasp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, they're so smart.\NBetter than the military ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm shocked for an entirely different reason.{僕は別のことの方がショックだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I raised Tenmaru and Chimaru\Nmyself ever since they were puppies,{てんまるとちまるは僕は子犬の頃から仕込んだんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but even then, they'd\Nrather listen to Benio than to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I thought it would end badly \Nfor a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say you haven't bathed in ten days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gross. At least take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly! If you say so, Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, I'd say Benio is doing remarkably well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have some guts\Nto have tamed the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let myself be tamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. Really, Benio never ceases to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everyone.{いや諸君すまなかったね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I spoiled the party with my sloppiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! You look brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, shall we drink?{さあ、飲み直しますか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... deeply sorry, but I'll be leaving now.{私せっかくだけどお先に失礼いたします}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tamaki, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling too well.{ちょっと気分が優れないもので}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It's a pity.\NThen, I'll tell our chauffeur to take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Th-Then, I'll escort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Tamaki, may I have the honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Riding with the beautiful Tamaki...{麗しのたまき殿と相乗りか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a ride. Tamaki needs to be\Nescorted home. Can you do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, please get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A rickshaw is such a fancy vehicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. That looks way more fun.{そうねそちらの方が面白そうだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, may we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Hop in, hop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always happy to help\Nthe Boss's friends! Jump right in!{N親分の友達だったら喜んでね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In this male-dominated world, shouldn't we abide\Nby our spheres of influence above anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yeah. Understood, Boss.{わかりやした親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear customers, unfortunately, \Ndriving you is not in my competence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You may use the car over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, but I really wanted to ride it once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Chauffeur, they're all yours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After the dogs, she won the chauffeur over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just an overbearing upstart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you admit\Nthat you've grown fond of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Sunday my day off on the schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you for a little different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right now and not a minute later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?{何かしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, you see...{はいそれがその}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just gotten this new maid who\Ninsisted on becoming your personal servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A new maid?{新しいメイドが}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From today onwards, \NLady Benio is your Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Greet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ranko. \NDelighted to meet you, Master.{らんこと申しますよろしくお願いしますご主人様}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ra-Ra-Ra-Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,An unexpected meeting \Nat an unexpected place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire to help by any means necessary\Ndrove the tormented Ranmaru to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So with her full feminine dedication—{女心を一筋}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... Should I say masculine resolve?{いや、男心というべきかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how will things play out for Ranko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire of the tormented beauty Ranmaru, \Nwho's now a maid in disguise,{悩ましの美少女がメイドに化けた蘭丸で}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to help Benio by any means necessary \Nis now becoming an inconvenience for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, he must do whatever\Nit takes to not reveal his true sex.{だが男女のその正体がもしもバレたら一大事に}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, thanks to his keen look, the Count immediately starts questioning Ranmaru's true identity.{さすが老伯爵の慧眼は}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this spells major trouble for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dance, Tormented Beauty"{踊れ悩ましの美少女}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
